691665472.text: "Immunoblotting analysis demonstrated that UCN-01 alone or in combination with irinotecan affects the ATR mediated phosphorylation of Chk1 and PKC directly blocking the activation of the Chk1 target CDC25C, confirming the contribution of several targets in determining the response of CRC-SCs to UCN-01."
